                       Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Gardening Confidential takes us on aninternational exploration of one of the 
most obsessive hobbies in human history, and discovers some surprising modern 
twists. From robotic lawnmowers to gardens on Mars, from trendy Manhattan 
rooftops to virtual gardens in cyberspace, this ancient craft has entered the 
space age and become a multi-billion dollar industry. Meet some of the most 
single-minded gardeners in the world and discover how gardening can get you in 
trouble with the law.
